/*
 * Generate time intelligence measures based
 *
 * Modified by: Reid Havens, https://havensconsulting.net 
 * Original Author(s): Benoit Fedit, https://datakuity.com 
 * Original Author(s): Bernat AgullÃ³, www.esbrina-ba.com/blog 
 *
